{"tid":1603543,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"十月一日民眾要高呼「天滅中共，全黨死清光」","createTime":"2019-09-29T16:55:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T19:40:27.000Z","uid":131157,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a0d05e0ffa87e70a06dc4cda1d4e81a85f519879","tid":1603543,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:55:54.000Z","msg":"十月一日，中共建政七十週年，中共進入風燭殘年的時候，正是香港人公開講出驅逐中共的大好時機，驅逐共黨，解放香港。香港人必須打破心理障礙，敢於高呼反共，共產黨是尊重民情的，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人這樣高呼，中共就會退走，放手給香港自治，反正香港自治也有利於共產黨開拓國際關係。但你不打中共，他們不會給你。</span></strong><br />\n目前的民主派、偽港獨派和商場唱歌派，全部不敢高呼反共，全部在講曖昧的「時代革命」，因為他們謀算的是在普選之後與共產黨和地產財閥勾結合作，繼續用議席凌駕香港人的政治發言權，繼續剝削香港。他們是暗共，是共產黨在香港的統治夥伴，有些更是共產黨直接扶植起來的。<br />\n<strong>我們民眾自己在十月一日高呼反共，傳閱崇禎上煤山吊頸圖，令共產黨知道香港的民意，知難而退。</strong><br />\n陳雲一直告訴各位，共產黨是非常現實的，中共的銀行和企業非常依賴香港來套取資金，中共的資產放在香港樓房產業和股市，香港人敢去高呼反共，咒罵共產黨死清光，他們就收斂起來，說不定一兩位共產黨元老會因為看到咒罵而灰心喪氣，甘願死去。<br />\n衙差見到你高呼反共，他們也會退避三舍，因為他們不想被香港人視為共產黨的爪牙，大家可以試試看。不要再叫什麼黑警、黑社會，這些只會令到衙差反感而打你，你高叫共產黨走狗、共產黨打手，他們就會知所進退。<br />\n請在十月一日之前，廣傳這個訊息。"},{"pid":"285a67fd8af5ff05c90802e83312fea2f6961026","tid":1603543,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:57:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"967cb69d1ff0c6bb72b89f7168c21cf6b89d3112","tid":1603543,"uid":197563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:58:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X0LcvJe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX0LcvJe.jpg&h=922a548d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YRhBXof.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYRhBXof.jpg&h=2ad29912&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/duHRMgA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FduHRMgA.jpg&h=c7d87c98&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8DBOOuW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8DBOOuW.jpg&h=a38bf149&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MxdtOuW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMxdtOuW.jpg&h=acc3caf5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X5vG8uX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX5vG8uX.jpg&h=286dbb12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"289590b35e2c3fa333645868e160866db6ad1781","tid":1603543,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T20:48:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca9b459f4bb48bb7e336da6c483dae377498fba","tid":1603543,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T20:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0218b25d5098be17ec6064721f10845ccf5cc5c9","tid":1603543,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T20:49:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c34c5814c09de043d011ab9545cbfc70b339a21","tid":1603543,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T20:49:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e098fcd51036fa8e4c8a27b354a004c67018464","tid":1603543,"uid":150267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep